            <localString languageId="0" >
                <value><![CDATA[Basics of Tailoring
Tailoring will require harden hides from tanners. The harden hides are made into colored cloths if used with dyes by a tailor.

Dyes
-----
To make clothes you must first Dye Hides from animals. You can use a variety of different colors of dye for a variety of effects. 

Hides
-----
Hardened medium and large hides can be used in tailoring. You must turn the hides into cloth using dye and the tailors knife.

Cloth
-------
There is alot of different kinds of cloth that can be made. Large cloth is used for armor and clothes, and medium cloth is used for everything else.]]></value>
